{"tid":2160404,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"反美斯班友咪痴撚線㗎！對球會忠誠就話人唔敢接受挑戰。","createTime":"2020-08-17T02:36:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-17T09:07:04.000Z","uid":43785,"like":12,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"522a1874da96c19d87718190dda6de7a69ccc641","tid":2160404,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T02:36:45.000Z","msg":"反美斯班友咪痴撚線㗎！<br />\n對球會忠誠就話人唔敢接受挑戰。<br />\n<br />\n屌你老母，不如話你賤種C朗拿度唔撚夠忠誠。敗走歐聯敗走西甲。<br />\nC朗究竟係挑戰定係敗走，明眼人都睇到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一生效力一個球隊，係一件忠誠嘅事。<br />\n你地班傻閪唔好鳩反啦。<br />\n你叫你個C朗學下咩叫忠誠先啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0472b6d7dbf2410ff3f3ec4f0b7f41510ad7c1c1","tid":2160404,"uid":229955,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T02:37:28.000Z","msg":"你點屌的？"},{"pid":"305945e5e90b4452b7f87eafa160a3ff25ab6fb7","tid":2160404,"uid":324246,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T02:38:03.000Z","msg":"你點接受的？"},{"pid":"4e1af3df7f615af190d3769bec686be39501458c","tid":2160404,"uid":301749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T02:38:43.000Z","msg":"你點忠誠的"},{"pid":"b8b5cbdd181be3a19451124738f2e47c3606e5a6","tid":2160404,"uid":233316,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T02:38:47.000Z","msg":"唔係巴狗比錢醫佢，美斯做緊馬戲團咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c864d713728e24e531e72b7ee70a538efe4ae79","tid":2160404,"uid":58209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T02:39:14.000Z","msg":"鳩sir早晨<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"873af360299f9c7a8578c0337f36e4b61f8e83c8","tid":2160404,